{"id": 2187, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些智能时代的不智能时刻会让你抓狂？", "description": "现如今一旦断网断电，我的生存能力比山顶洞人还不如。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 8291, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180222122455K0nLoilDfaUpQT7G.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-22T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3763, "title": "哪些智能时代的不智能时刻会让你抓狂？", "content": "哪些智能时代的不智能时刻会让你抓狂？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 266114, "content": "智能门锁连不上网或者app出bug，打不开门干着急", "image": "img/option/option/20180222131550jrNUhI5RKXS1P0HO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266121, "content": "电子下单寄快递，快递员打不熟练半天打印不出快递单", "image": "img/option/option/20180222131601RnSxPENzrOd6jfyI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266124, "content": "刷手机出地铁，出站口信号不好刷不出", "image": "img/option/option/20180222131717k38QDzpixmloy5tH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266125, "content": "语音助手听不全问题，一个劲装懂“这是个好问题”", "image": "img/option/option/20180222131733KBtYHyNUhXVQwabO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266129, "content": "智能音箱不能连续对话，每次必须“叮咚叮咚”“天猫精灵”", "image": "img/option/option/20180222131747hFnA41avQbEfwZM7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266130, "content": "开车抄近路，语音导航得絮叨五分钟快掉头", "image": "img/option/option/20180222131800RBpdz1DKlm6oHvrj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266132, "content": "智能体感车一旦质量不佳/出bug会摔很惨", "image": "img/option/option/20180222132015ADPJSusEw9CfgeaU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266133, "content": "智能电视甚至不能按需设置频道顺序", "image": "img/option/option/201802221321070bGSHWy87ijk6MX1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}